 625→`PermissionMode` controls the security level for forge pipeline execution:
 626→- **Readonly**: Only read-only tools available
 627→- **Standard**: Auto-approve iterations below a file-change threshold
 628→- **Autonomous**: Auto-approve all iterations
 629→- **Strict**: Documented as "requires manual approval every iteration"
